data.description: BACK ON MARKET at no fault of Seller! Check out this  amazing, well maintained 3 Bedrooms/2 Bath home features a large great room with high ceilings and hardwood flooring throughout the main living areas, a fully equipped, open kitchen with a breakfast area, pantry, refrigerator/icemaker, gas stove, built in microwave, dishwasher and wiring for a garbage disposal, if desired. The adjacent sunroom has tons of windows with lots of natural light. The private, fenced backyard features a great 16 X 20 she-shed/workshop/detached garage with power, side entry door, overhead roll up door w/ramp and work bench. Added features include newer vinyl windows throughout the home; Trane HVAC and newer deck. HOA includes a Community Pool and Picnic Area. Convenient to schools, shopping in both McDonough, Locust Grove, and to Hwy 42 and I-75.
